OL,3,COnly one in six children learning
OL,4,Crecorder after drop in popularity over
OL,5,Cdecade
OL,7,FOnly around one in six children now
OL,8,Flearns the recorder after a decline in
OL,9,Fits popularity over the past decade, a
OL,10,Fnew report suggests.
OL,12,FHowever, the paper by the ABRSM, the
OL,13,Fexam board of the Royal Schools of
OL,14,FMusic, suggests the range of
OL,15,Finstruments now being taught is
OL,16,F"widening".
OL,18,FThe study compares the results of a
OL,19,Fnew survey of more than 1,000 children
OL,20,Faged five to 17 with research carried
OL,21,Fout by the charity previously.
