OL,5,Cdecade
OL,7,FIt reveals that 16% of children said
OL,8,Fthey played the recorder in 2024, down
OL,9,Ffrom 28% in 2014.
OL,11,FThe report said: "Instrument choice
OL,12,Fand the range of instruments taught by
OL,13,Fmusic teachers is widening, reflecting
OL,14,Fboth a shift in learner tastes and the
OL,15,Fneed for music teachers to respond to
OL,16,Fthis."
