OL,5,Cdecade
OL,7,FThe piano and keyboard remain the most
OL,8,Fpopular instruments that children
OL,9,Flearn to play, but the electric
OL,10,Fguitar, drums, flute, violin and
OL,11,Fukulele have also become more popular
OL,12,Famong young people compared with
OL,13,Fprevious years.
OL,15,FOverall, 17% of children said they
OL,16,Fplay the electric guitar, up from 13%
OL,17,Fin 2014, and 15% of children play the
OL,18,Fflute, up from just 7% in 2014, the
OL,19,Freport found.
