OL,7,FShifts are "likely to reflect trends
OL,8,Fin instrumental tuition at school", as
OL,9,Fwell as a wider range of instruments
OL,10,Fbeing offered by private music
OL,11,Fteachers, it added.
OL,13,FThe report said the recorder is one of
OL,14,Fthe most "given up" instruments.
OL,16,FPiano (16%), keyboard (13%) and
OL,17,Frecorder (11%) are the most common
OL,18,Finstruments that respondents said they
OL,19,Fpreviously played but no longer do.
