OL,7,FABRSM chief executive Chris Cobb said:
OL,8,F"Children get to play an instrument
OL,9,Ffor the first time in large classes.
OL,11,F"The recorder has been great for that
OL,12,Fbut schools are now looking at other
OL,13,Finstruments that can be used ` the
OL,14,Fukulele and acoustic guitar among
OL,15,Fthem. Singing is also a key part of
OL,16,Fwhole-class music-making."
