OL,7,FHe added: "The mental health benefits
OL,8,Fof music are hugely important at a
OL,9,Ftime when mental illness is so rife
OL,10,Fbut there are so many other benefits
OL,11,Ftoo.
OL,13,F"The tragedy is that the same research
OL,14,Fshows how young people disengage from
OL,15,Fmusic learning, both when they shift
OL,16,Fto secondary school and when they
OL,17,Fstart GCSEs.
